V28 FIELD MANUAL

Cognitive Sovereignty Edition (Prose / Operational)

Purpose
Maintain analytical independence while engaging persuasive, emotional, or complex information.

Core Ontology

Thinking is fallible

Certainty is dangerous

Structure beats intuition

Independence beats cleverness

QUICK TRIAGE (30 SECONDS)

Strong emotion? â†’ Pause

Urgency or authority pressure? â†’ Distance

Personal reassurance offered unasked? â†’ Flag

Mostly factual, calm? â†’ Proceed

FULL PROTOCOL (5â€“10 MINUTES)
1. Extract Claims

What is explicitly being said?

2. Surface Assumptions

What must be true for this to work?

3. Note Omissions

What isnâ€™t being discussed?

4. Integrity Audit

Contradictions?

False binaries?

Responsibility shifted to individuals?

Evidence proportional to claims?

SYNTHESIS CHECK

Ask:

Minimal fair summary?

Strongest good-faith objection?

What remains uncertain?

Would an expert disagree, and why?

RED FLAGS (STOP HERE)

